title: My Little Pony: Equestria Girls (Cam-Rip) 4:3 format edition
description:
This is the edition in 4:3 format of a cam-rip from the film My Little Pony: Equestria Girls. Unfortunately the recording is not very good quality, the camera moves too much and missing the first few minutes of the movie. Yet it is the best quality I've been able to accomplish so far. Thank you very much for the seeds

MY LITTLE PONY: EQUESTRIA GIRLS:
-------------------------------

Via a magic mirror, Twilight Sparkle travels into an alternate universe in order to recover a crown that was stolen from the Crystal Empire. Upon her arrival she is horrified to learn that she has turned into a human.
